# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore for The Pure Go Standard Library Stack
#
# This file is organized into sections for clarity and maintainability.
# It covers build artifacts, local configurations, and common OS/IDE files.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Build Artifacts & Binaries ---
# Compiled Go binaries and local build outputs.
/bin/
/build/

# --- Local Configuration & Environment ---
# Environment files contain sensitive credentials and should never be committed.
# A `.env.example` file should be committed instead to define required variables.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Local Database Files ---
# The SQLite database file and its related journal/WAL files.
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# --- Development Tools & Logs ---
# Log files.
*.log

# Go test coverage and profiling files.
*.out
*.prof
*.test
/coverage/

# --- IDE & Editor Configuration ---
# User-specific settings for common editors.

# Visual Studio Code
.vscode/

# JetBrains (GoLand, IntelliJ)
.idea/

# Vim & Neovim
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Sublime Text
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# --- Operating System Files ---
# Files generated automatically by different operating systems.

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
__MACOSX/

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# Linux
.directory
